====================
ABOUT
====================

charset is a c++ template library that allows you to convert data between different character encoding in easy way.

================
DOCUMENTATION
================

Refer to DOC file for documentation.

====================
HOW TO USE
====================

Simply include "charset.hpp" and link to charset.a or charset.lib based on the compiler you use.

====================
EXAMPLES
====================

Refer to TUTOR file, but before doing that make sure to read the documentation to understand how examples work.

====================
DEVELOPEMENT
====================

Track development changes at charset.sourceforge.net
